Usun-Kyuyol (; , Uhun Küöl) is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Sylansky Rural Okrug in Churapchinsky District of the Sakha Republic, Russia, located  from Churapcha, the administrative center of the district. Its population as of the 2010 Census was 751; down from 863 recorded in the 2002 Census.
